parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the key to stick or fall out while driving, leading to loss of control and potential accidents.
symptoms: The key can be removed from the ignition switch while the vehicle is running
the key turns extremely hard
the key can be pulled out before the ignition switch reaches the off position
and the ignition switch gets stuck while parked.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power steering, and experience issues with the airbag system, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The instrument cluster and radio/dash lights go out
the vehicle stalls
power steering is lost
smoke is seen coming from under the hood
and electrical wires under the fuse box catch fire.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause the airbags to deploy unexpectedly or not deploy at all in the event of a crash, which can lead to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag light stays on
the passenger airbag indicator light is on even when the seat is occupied
and the airbag system malfunctions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door latch can cause the doors to become stuck, making it difficult or impossible to exit the vehicle in an emergency, which can lead to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The doors are stuck shut
the door latch mechanism fails
and the doors cannot be opened from the inside or outside.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to the non-deployment of airbags in the event of an accident, increasing the risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates
the passenger airbag indicator light does not turn on when a passenger is in the seat
the airbag warning light flashes or remains on
and the airbag system fails to deploy in the event of an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the key to get stuck, making it difficult or impossible to start the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The key gets stuck in the ignition switch
the key won't turn
the steering wheel locks
the key has to be jiggled to turn
the ignition switch has to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering can cause the vehicle to be difficult to steer, making it hard to control, which can lead to accidents.
symptoms: The power steering fails
the steering wheel is hard to turn
the steering wheel shakes
the vehicle vibrates
the power steering rack needs to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle's lights and accessories to malfunction, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The interior and exterior lights flash on and off
the radio turns on and off
the locks on the doors lock and unlock repeatedly
the power steering stops working
the alternator fails.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering column can cause the steering wheel to lock, making it difficult or impossible to steer, which can lead to accidents.
symptoms: The steering wheel locks
the key gets stuck in the ignition switch
the steering column has to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rust and corrosion can cause the vehicle's structural integrity to be compromised, which can lead to accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle is very rusted out
the underneath of the body is rusted
the vehicle is a hazard to drive and work on.
